{
  "texts": [
    "\"As shown in Fig. 1, the recent research of foundation models has enabled the AI models to learn general abilities and be applied to wide healthcare scenarios, giving a promising answer to this question [9]- [12].",
    "In the related sub-fields of healthcare AI, including language, vision, bioinformatics, and multi-modality, the healthcare foundation model (HFM) has shown impressive success.",
    "a) Language foundation model (LFM) or named large language model (LLM) [13], [14] has caused excitement and concern for the benefit of patients and clinicians [13].",
    "It learned large-scale medical language data, and has shown extraordinary performance in medical text processing [15] and dialogue [16] tasks.",
    "b) Vision foundation model (VFM) has demonstrated remarkable potential in medical images."
  ]
}